                            <div class="detail">
                                <div class="litleDesc">With senior managers from over 20 different nationalities, making sure everyone shared the same sense of purpose was the goal for one of the world’s leading oil drilling multinationals.</div>
                                <div class="infoCompany">	
                                    <span>Company:</span>	Energy Multinational				<br><span>Country:</span>	Worldwide				<br><span>Employees:</span>	18,000+							</div>

                                <div class="usedServices">
                                    <span>Main Key Services :</span>

                                    <a href="http://www.phoenixobsidian.com/#communication-management" title="Communication, 
                                       Management &amp; Leadership Skills"> 
                                        <img src="img/case-studies_mini_mini_sphere_service_communication-management.png" width="103" height="86">
                                    </a><a></a><a href="http://www.phoenixobsidian.com/#facilitation-team-development" title="Facilitation, 
                                                  Team &amp; Group Development"> 
                                        <img src="img/case-studies_mini_mini_sphere_service_facilitation-team-group.png" width="103" height="86">
                                    </a><a></a><a href="http://www.phoenixobsidian.com/#vision-mission-definition" title="Vision &amp; Mission Definition"> 
                                        <img src="img/case-studies_mini_mini_sphere_service_vision-mission-definition.png" width="103" height="86">
                                    </a><a></a>				<!--
    <a href="#facilitation-team-development" title="View service : Facilitation, Team & Group Development"><img src="templates/medias/case-studies_mini_mini_sphere_service_facilitation-team-group.png" width="103" height="86"/></a>
    <a href="#change-management-consultancy" title="View service : Change Management &amp; Consultancy"><img src="templates/medias/case-studies_mini_mini_sphere_service_change-management.png" width="103" height="86"/></a>
