                            <div class="detail">
                                <div class="litleDesc">A clash of cultures at a Swiss pharmaceutical was avoided with a two-speed approach to team-building and a clever use of PowerPoint.</div>
                                <div class="infoCompany">	
                                    <span>Company:</span>	Swiss Pharmaceutical Giant				<br><span>Country:</span>	Worldwide 				<br><span>Employees:</span>	120,000+							</div>

                                <div class="usedServices">
                                    <span>Main Key Services :</span>

