                            <div class="slide slide1">
                                <h1>Jim Peal</h1>
                                <img src="img/jim_peale.png" alt="Jim Peal" width="287" height="385">
                                <h2>Bio</h2>
                                <div>Jim’s expertise in managing culture change, inspiring leaders and energising teams has been successfully used by leading companies across a wide range of sectors, including manufacturing, utilities, pharmaceutical &amp; biotech, technology and retail.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    Over the course of his 20-year career, Jim has also found the time to serve on the board of various organisations, including Miramar, Inc. and the Santa Barbara Graduate Institute. He has additionally published these three acclaimed books on culture change and leadership: Power Tools…The Fast Track to Success, Daring to Have Real Conversations at Work and Check Your Attitude at the Door.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    His impressive client list includes Levi Strauss, Disney, GlaxoSmithKline, Johnson &amp; Johnson, ConocoPhillips, Pfizer, Roche, Merck, Edison International, Taco Bell and The University of California.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    Jim lives in Oakland, California.</div>
                                <h2>Professionnal Qualifications</h2>
