                            <div class="slide slide1">
                                <h1>Jane Anglin</h1>
                                <img src="img/jane_anglin.png" alt="Jane Anglin" width="287" height="385">
                                <h2>Bio</h2>
                                <div>Jane has over 25 years’ experience working with blue-chip companies to develop a vision for the future and practical strategies to ensure that vision succeeds.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    Recent successful projects include designing and managing a two-year development programme for Standard Life Savings; developing a People programme for the launch of Lloyds Bank Insurance Direct, and creating a culture change strategy for Alliance &amp; Leicester, Girobank.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    Other clients include Nationwide Building Society, Britannia Building Society and Getty Images.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    Jane lives in the UK.</div>
                                <h2>Professionnal Qualifications</h2>
                                <div><ul>
                                        <li>
                                            MSc in Change Agent Skill and Strategies</li>
                                        <li>
                                            Member of the International Coaching Federation</li>
                                        <li>
