                            <div class="slide slide1">
                                <h1>Patricia Bouvard</h1>
                                <img src="img/patricia-bouvard.png" alt="Patricia Bouvard" width="287" height="385">
                                <h2>Bio</h2>
                                <div>Before specialising in leadership, management and customer change issues, Patricia was a senior executive in the international cosmetics and fashion sectors working for Givenchy, Paco Rabanne, Pierre Balmain, Caron and Revillon among others.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    For the last 13 years, she has worked with the senior management of multinationals to transform their organisations to enable everyone to perform better. Renowned for her energetic and innovative approach, Patricia has pioneered a number of highly creative techniques including the Persona Method that uses masks from the 14th century Commedia dell’Arte to transform people’s behaviour.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    On top of her change management work, Patricia has co-founded a number of successful companies including Horizon Performance Conseil and Forest Consulting.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    Recent clients include LVMH, Karl Storz, HP-Compaq, UBS, Eli Lilly, Amazon, Axa, Altana Pharma, Cephalon, Airbus/EADS, Novo Nordisk and the Montpellier International Business School.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    She lives in Nimes, France.</div>
