                                <h1>Trish Barron</h1>
                                <img src="img/trish-barron.png" alt="Trish Barron" width="287" height="385">
                                <h2>Bio</h2>
                                <div>Trish is a highly respected senior level consultant and coach with over 20 years’ experience helping companies and individuals achieve long-lasting and profitable change. Acclaimed for her compassion, talent and direct approach, she is renowned for encouraging her clients to tackle difficult issues to produce high impact results across a broad mix of sectors from defence and FMCG to manufacturing and biotech. She has also worked with a number of non-profit and government bodies.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    Trish specialises in developing the skills of leaders and senior managers, group facilitation, conflict resolution and encouraging powerful communication across entire organisations.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    Recent clients include GlaxoSmithKline, Duke University, Blue Cross and Blue Shield, National Nuclear Security Administration, Genentech, Red Hat and UMICORE, Inc.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    Trish lives in North Carolina.</div>
