                    <div class="content">
                        <h1>Endorsements</h1>


                        <div class="pages">
                            <div class="rendu">
                                <h2 class="facilitation-team-development">Facilitation, 
                                    Team &amp; Group Development</h2>
                                <p class="facilitation-team-development">
                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>
                                    I want to say thank you for a fantastic job with the Team. Let's put it this way - I was impressed with your work with the first team, but Regulatory Affairs is a very different ball game. For me the stakes are much higher because I have a significant accountability here compared to any other leadership team. To hear guys say “it was a great use of our time and we are glad we did it" is huge progress. There's your credibility right there.				<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">VP HR, Global Pharmaceutical</p>
                            </div><!--END rendu -->

                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="facilitation-team-development" endorsementnumberquote="23">
                                <h2 class="facilitation-team-development">Facilitation, 
                                    Team &amp; Group Development</h2>
                                <p class="facilitation-team-development"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>I want to say thank you for a fantastic job with the Team. Let's put it this way - I was impressed with your work with the first team, but Regulatory Affairs is a very different ball game. For me the stakes are much higher because I have a significant accountability here compared to any other leadership team. To hear guys say “it was a great use of our time and we are glad we did it" is huge progress. There's your credibility right there.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">VP HR, Global Pharmaceutical</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="facilitation-team-development" endorsementnumberquote="31">
                                <h2 class="facilitation-team-development">Facilitation, 
                                    Team &amp; Group Development</h2>
                                <p class="facilitation-team-development"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>I think the most useful way in which I have been helped is to try to look at things from others’ point of view and specifically the reaction in others to my own actions.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">Richard Binks, DMG Pinnacle</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="facilitation-team-development" endorsementnumberquote="109">
                                <h2 class="facilitation-team-development">Facilitation, 
                                    Team &amp; Group Development</h2>
                                <p class="facilitation-team-development"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>How many senior executives does it take to change a light bulb? Depends on the facilitator. That’s my view after seeing Thom at work. When I asked him to facilitate a very important leadership team meeting, he worked closely with me to plan every detail, design the agenda and look out for potential pitfalls that might derail us. He also ensured everyone taking part agreed to the objectives before we began. Thanks to Thom’s expert knowledge and hard work, the meeting was extremely productive and rewarding. What’s more, his light touch and easy manner made us all feel it was our success.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">CFO, Multinational Energy Company</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="executive-coaching" endorsementnumberquote="152">
                                <h2 class="executive-coaching">Executive Coaching</h2>
                                <p class="executive-coaching"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>The experience of coaching far exceeded my initial expectations of potentially improving my operational performance. It enabled a sense of peace and relaxation with my work that I had never experienced before and thus greater personal performance.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">Senior Manager, Major Global Computer Corporation</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="executive-coaching" endorsementnumberquote="235">
                                <h2 class="executive-coaching">Executive Coaching</h2>
                                <p class="executive-coaching"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>We have discussions and you pick detail and ask questions and I get to the crux of the matter. As a result ‘coaching’ gives me a more balanced objective view and helps me face issues which, in my job, it is difficult to discuss with anyone else competent to comment without being indiscreet.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">MD, Packaging Machinery Company</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="executive-coaching" endorsementnumberquote="216">
                                <h2 class="executive-coaching">Executive Coaching</h2>
                                <p class="executive-coaching"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>Thom came at a time in my career where I needed the counsel and wisdom of a man who had been there and got the T-shirt! Thom has a great listening style and the ability to help you deconstruct the issues you may be facing and guides you to possible solution pathways. I know my line manager saw an immediate change in my interactions with my peers and leaders and using his words - I became more comfortable in my skin. I would have no hesitation in recommending Thom Dennis and his organisation.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">Professor Luigi G Martini</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="communication-management" endorsementnumberquote="237">
                                <h2 class="communication-management">Communication, 
                                    Management &amp; Leadership Skills</h2>
                                <p class="communication-management"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>[Phoenix Obsidian has] educated me to look at the big picture, to plan and execute day-to-day management duties more effectively and in a more professional manner. My approach, I feel, will never be the same. I found that above all we are all human beings at the end of the day and should honour others by treating them in the way they wish to be treated.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">Graham Evans, The Cable Corporation</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="communication-management" endorsementnumberquote="100">
                                <h2 class="communication-management">Communication, 
                                    Management &amp; Leadership Skills</h2>
                                <p class="communication-management"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>The Program has helped me to be more confident in my job, not only in dealing with other members of the team but also in making presentations, attending meetings, etc. This has been the most useful course I have ever attended and been able to put into use.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">Barbara McShane, The Cable Corporation</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="communication-management" endorsementnumberquote="63">
                                <h2 class="communication-management">Communication, 
                                    Management &amp; Leadership Skills</h2>
                                <p class="communication-management"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span> The only management course which cannot be dismissed as ‘management bullshit’ by anyone. <br>
                                    The reason ? Because the objectives which you leave with are set by you&nbsp;!&nbsp;<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">Paul Johnson, Telewest</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="change-management-consultancy" endorsementnumberquote="251">
                                <h2 class="change-management-consultancy">Change Management &amp; Consultancy</h2>
                                <p class="change-management-consultancy"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>I cannot tell you how reassuring it is to have someone to simply call and discuss an issue with, to bounce ideas off, in the knowledge that you will get a rational, experienced and unbiased opinion. All I can say is there is nothing more sobering or invigorating than the clarity of an objective view which quickly flushes out real issues and personal bias. The balance Thom brought to our team cannot be overestimated.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">MD, Communications Firm</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="change-management-consultancy" endorsementnumberquote="192">
                                <h2 class="change-management-consultancy">Change Management &amp; Consultancy</h2>
                                <p class="change-management-consultancy"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>The frankness, honesty and informality you encourage during the sessions has made them something from which I have drawn great strength during a difficult time. I have learnt techniques and practical skills that have helped me to maintain a clear head throughout a very difficult time of change, and keep my staff motivated and happy.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">Customer Services Manager, Printing Company</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="change-management-consultancy" endorsementnumberquote="154">
                                <h2 class="change-management-consultancy">Change Management &amp; Consultancy</h2>
                                <p class="change-management-consultancy"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>We operate in many different countries around the world – each with a unique culture. It was crucial that our own culture was strong enough to adapt to local differences without losing our corporate identity. After listening to our goals, Thom and his team drew on their extensive experience of working with people from across the globe to devise and implement a change programme that means today the whole company speaks with one voice – regardless of our accent.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">Head of Strategic Planning, Global Energy Company</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="vision-mission-definition" endorsementnumberquote="202">
                                <h2 class="vision-mission-definition">Vision &amp; Mission Definition</h2>
                                <p class="vision-mission-definition"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>The results have been incredibly pleasing. This is the biggest shift in attitudes and behavior that I have ever seen take place as a result of a single meeting. <br>
                                    It has really made a huge difference to the results we are seeing in the business.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">SVP of a Global Energy Company</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="vision-mission-definition" endorsementnumberquote="59">
                                <h2 class="vision-mission-definition">Vision &amp; Mission Definition</h2>
                                <p class="vision-mission-definition"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>Without doubt, and it is solely attributable to your very sensitive and diplomatic style, I am convinced that the twelve hours that we spent together … provided some of the most helpful and practical advice and guidance that I have ever received. True, you made me work very hard to get down to the real issues, but the processes that you employ create an environment that is creative, stimulating, satisfying and rewarding.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">MD, Computer Storage Company</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="slide" endorsementservice="vision-mission-definition" endorsementnumberquote="47">
                                <h2 class="vision-mission-definition">Vision &amp; Mission Definition</h2>
                                <p class="vision-mission-definition"> 

                                    <span class="before">&nbsp;</span>What impressed me was you never backed away from the direct and more importantly indirect/unspoken challenges thrown at you. That's when I knew I was watching and learning from a master ... you're really good Thom. You're a pleasure to work with.<span class="after">&nbsp;</span>				
                                </p>
                                <p class="author">VP HR, Global Pharmaceutical</p>
                            </div>

